    {
        "content": "<p>This looks like an aligned SIMD load used on an un-aligned memory address. The probable cause is either that some abstraction in <a href=\"https://juliaregistries.github.io/General/packages/redirect_to_repo/SIMD\">SIMD.jl</a> incorrectly emits an aligned load, or that <a href=\"https://juliaregistries.github.io/General/packages/redirect_to_repo/TiffImages\">TiffImages.jl</a> manually asks for an aligned load where inappropriate.</p>",
        "id": 587765570,
        "sender_full_name": "Jakob Nybo Andersen",
        "timestamp": 1776691527
    },
    {
